# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# RAI v6.0 Environment Variables
# 이 파일을 .env.local로 복사하고 값을 채워주세요
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Supabase
# https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/YOUR_PROJECT/settings/api
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# Service Role Key (서버 사이드에서만 사용, 절대 클라이언트에 노출 금지)
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI API Keys (Phase 1 & 2)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# OpenAI (GPT-4o, text-embedding-3-small)
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key

# Google AI (Gemini 1.5 Pro)
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-google-ai-key

# Anthropic (Claude 3.5 Sonnet) - Phase 2 / Enterprise
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-key

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Encryption (AES-256-GCM)
# 32바이트 키 (64자 hex) - 반드시 안전하게 보관!
# 생성: openssl rand -hex 32
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ENCRYPTION_KEY=b0f7e07a3e89c6a52459f895bb2a2cd78d83e1492d64bb5702648c001e08cfa6

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Redis Queue (Upstash)
# https://console.upstash.com/redis
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=https://your-redis.upstash.io
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=your-upstash-token

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Payment (Stripe) - Phase 1.5+
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_your-stripe-key
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_your-webhook-secret
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_your-publishable-key

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# App Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000

# 분석 모드 (phase_1 or phase_2)
ANALYSIS_MODE=phase_1

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Worker API (Python FastAPI on Railway)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
WORKER_URL=http://localhost:8000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional: Hancom API (HWP 파싱 3차 Fallback)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HANCOM_API_KEY=your-hancom-api-key

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Error Tracking (Sentry)
# https://sentry.io/settings/YOUR_ORG/projects/YOUR_PROJECT/keys/
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=https://xxx@xxx.ingest.sentry.io/xxx
# SENTRY_ORG=your-org
# SENTRY_PROJECT=your-project

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Development
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NODE_ENV=development
